Package: diaper
Type: Package
Title: A Lightweight Way To Catalogue Project Dependencies
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: c(person(c("Zhian N."), "Kamvar", role = c("cre", "aut"), email = "zkamvar@gmail.com"))
Maintainer: Zhian N. Kamvar <zkamvar@gmail.com>
Description: This package is a lightweight method of creating a DESCRIPTION file for listing project
            dependencies. This DESCRIPTION file can be used to signal devtools to install the dependencies.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
